comments.body:
The attached patch works with a single versions:set invocation, i.e.:

{code}
$ mvn versions:set -DnewVersion=0.24.1-SNAPSHOT 
{code}

Note that a few MR modules are using a property/variable to define the version of common/hdfs they are using and because of that the 'versions:set' does not take care of those. The correct thing to do there (IMO as part of another JIRA) is to make all those deps to use dependency management defined in the hadoop-project/pom.xml.
